image_analysis.description: A photograph of a closet or storage area. The image shows a white shelving unit with eight cubbies, some containing white storage bins. On top of the shelving unit are two stacks of thin white boxes, four boxes in each stack. Above the shelving unit is a white shelf with a metal hanging rod underneath. On the upper shelf, there are several black binders. The floor is covered with a light-colored patterned carpet. A white shopping bag is visible in the foreground.
image_analysis.layout: Interior storage space with shelving and organized boxes.
